{"tha-ap472:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap472:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap472:0.3":"Nimittabyakaraniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap472:1.1":"“Ajjhogahetva himavam, ","tha-ap472:1.2":"mante vace maham tada; ","tha-ap472:1.3":"Catupannasasahassani, ","tha-ap472:1.4":"sissa mayham upatthahum. ","tha-ap472:2.1":"Adhita vedagu sabbe, ","tha-ap472:2.2":"chalange paramim gata; ","tha-ap472:2.3":"Sakavijjahupatthaddha, ","tha-ap472:2.4":"himavante vasanti te. ","tha-ap472:3.1":"Cavitva tusita kaya, ","tha-ap472:3.2":"devaputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap472:3.3":"Uppajji matukucchismim, ","tha-ap472:3.4":"sampajano patissato. ","tha-ap472:4.1":"Sambuddhe upapajjante, ","tha-ap472:4.2":"dasasahassi kampatha; ","tha-ap472:4.3":"Andha cakkhum alabhimsu, ","tha-ap472:4.4":"uppajjantamhi nayake. ","tha-ap472:5.1":"Sabbakaram pakampittha, ","tha-ap472:5.2":"kevala vasudha ayam; ","tha-ap472:5.3":"Nigghosasaddam sutvana, ","tha-ap472:5.4":"ubbijjimsu mahajana. ","tha-ap472:6.1":"Sabbe jana samagamma, ","tha-ap472:6.2":"agacchum mama santikam; ","tha-ap472:6.3":"‘Vasudhayam pakampittha, ","tha-ap472:6.4":"kim vipako bhavissati’. ","tha-ap472:7.1":"Avacasim tada tesam, ","tha-ap472:7.2":"‘ma bhetha natthi vo bhayam; ","tha-ap472:7.3":"Vissattha hotha sabbepi, ","tha-ap472:7.4":"uppadoyam suvatthiko. ","tha-ap472:8.1":"Atthahetuhi samphussa, ","tha-ap472:8.2":"vasudhayam pakampati; ","tha-ap472:8.3":"Tatha nimitta dissanti, ","tha-ap472:8.4":"obhaso vipulo maha. ","tha-ap472:9.1":"Asamsayam buddhasettho, ","tha-ap472:9.2":"uppajjissati cakkhuma’; ","tha-ap472:9.3":"Sannapetvana janatam, ","tha-ap472:9.4":"panca sile kathesaham. ","tha-ap472:10.1":"Sutvana panca silani, ","tha-ap472:10.2":"buddhuppadanca dullabham; ","tha-ap472:10.3":"Ubbegajata sumana, ","tha-ap472:10.4":"tutthahattha ahamsu te. ","tha-ap472:11.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap472:11.2":"yam nimittam viyakarim; ","tha-ap472:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap472:11.4":"byakaranassidam phalam. ","tha-ap472:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap472:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap472:12.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap472:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap472:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap472:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap472:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap472:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap472:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap472:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nimittabyakaraniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap472:16.1":"Nimittabyakaraniyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap472:17.1":"Salakusumiyavaggo sattacattalisamo. ","tha-ap472:18.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap472:19.1":"Salakusumiyo thero, ","tha-ap472:19.2":"puja nibbapakopi ca; ","tha-ap472:19.3":"Setudo talavanti ca, ","tha-ap472:19.4":"avatalabujappado. ","tha-ap472:20.1":"Pilakkhapatibhani ca, ","tha-ap472:20.2":"veyyakaraniyo dijo; ","tha-ap472:20.3":"Dvesattati ca gathayo, ","tha-ap472:20.4":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}